lead_paragraph: Milwaukee starter Matt Garza left after 3 1/3 innings because right shoulder tightness, and the Brewers completed spring training with a 4-2 loss to the Houston Astros on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Brewers' Garza Leaves Start Because of Shoulder Tightness
